<p><img data-pin-nopin="nopin" alt='' src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20125%20125'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/116262146f6e1f5b08ee6edc91bc2141bc469e593256951135ade9535300d0b8?s=250&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-125 photo' height='125' width='125' decoding='async' data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/116262146f6e1f5b08ee6edc91bc2141bc469e593256951135ade9535300d0b8?s=125&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g"/><noscript><img data-pin-nopin="nopin" alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/116262146f6e1f5b08ee6edc91bc2141bc469e593256951135ade9535300d0b8?s=125&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/116262146f6e1f5b08ee6edc91bc2141bc469e593256951135ade9535300d0b8?s=250&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-125 photo' height='125' width='125' decoding='async'/></noscript>I'm Shana, the creator of Im-Worthy.com, capturing life's beauty through food stories. As a food photographer and writer, I empower busy women with easy plant-based and vegan recipes for vibrant, healthy living.  <a class="pagelink" href="https://im-worthy.com/about/">MORE ABOUT ME →</a></p>
